    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade FD3S featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with verified high compression across all rotor faces. This specimen retains its complex sequential twin-turbocharger architecture, providing a seamless transition and peak boost pressure without the typical vacuum-side boost leaks. The chassis is exceptionally tight, utilizing its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential for neutral handling. The 5-speed manual transmission exhibits precise gate engagement with no synchro grind. This is a thermally-sound, mechanically-synchronized example of 90s JDM engineering at its zenith.",
